rows.label: qst710204_msg0001
rows.name:
I've been waiting for you.
Did you catch any fish?

rows.label: qst710204_msg0102
rows.name:
I can't believe you
managed to get so many!

rows.label: qst710204_msg0103
rows.name:
OK, just a mo... The moat will
be back to normal in no time.

rows.label: qst710204_msg0201
rows.name:
Yeah, we'll need a few more fish than
that to do a moat that big justice. Do
you think you could get a few more?

rows.label: qst710204_msg0202
rows.name:
I'm especially looking for a big fish
with fierce fangs. Should appeal to
the Iirans' rambunctious nature!
